get-mailbox -identity <mailbox> | fl *rulesquota*
 
PS C:\Users\burnettc> set-mailbox -identity powells@b2b.regn.net -RulesQuota 256kb
PS C:\Users\burnettc> get-mailbox -identity powells@b2b.regn.net |fl *rulesquota*
 
 
RulesQuota : 256 KB (262,144 bytes)
 
 
